        "textSample": "Ciao Baby! Menu Private Parties About Visit Call “Burnt pasta. Their specialty.” The menu has real Barrington favorites: stuffed artichoke, Aunt Dodie’s eggplant, lamb chops Vesuvio, CiaoBaby! Burnt Pasta, chicken parmesan, gnocchi, and carrot cake. 4.5 (324 Reviews) Menu CIAOBABY! STARTERS Ciao Baby! Sticks Two generous breadsticks stuffed with mozzarella, dipped in garlic butter and herbs, served with marinara. $10 Stuffed Artichoke A family favorite with garlic breadcrumbs, parmesan, fragrant herbs, and a light broth. $16 Aunt Dodie’s Rolled Stuffed Eggplant Eggplant rolled around ricotta and mozzarella, topped with marinara and herbs. $18 Lamb Chops Vesuvio Four lollipop lamb chops sautéed in Vesuvio sauce and herbs, served over risotto. $24 CiaoBaby! Burnt Pasta Fried angel hair pasta sautéed in butter and marinara until crispy and burnt. $15 SALADS & FAMILY FAVORITES Very Chopped Meatless Salad Finely chopped greens, vegetables, gorgonzola, pasta, toffee nuts, and mango chardonnay dressing. $15 / $26 Umbriago Salad Chopped romaine with egg whites, tomato, cucumber, grilled asparagus, chicken, croutons, parmesan, and black pepper. $15 / $26 Stuffed Melrose Peppers Melrose pepp",
